<p>Dear <%= @chapter.user.username %><br/>
  You have been asked to write chapter <%= @chapter.number %> of "<%= @chapter.book.title %>".
</p>
<% if @chapter.number == 1 or @chapter.book.chapters[@chapter.number-2].state == "accepted" %>
<p>
Please log into our site to start writing.  When you are done writing,
select the "Finished" button.  We will send the chapter to your editor
for review.
</p><p>
<%= link_to "Click here to write your chapter.",  :controller => "book", :action =>"editBook", :id => @chapter.book, :only_path => false  %>
</p>
<% else %>
<p>The previous chapters are not yet complete.  You will receive a new email
message when the book is ready for you to write.
</p>
<% end %>
<p>
Have a great time writing,</br>
<%= @chapter.book.project.owner.username %> and The Book Project Team
</p>
